  "leve": {
    "name": "Growing Up",
    "description": "I work all day and barely have two gil to rub together at the end of it. I gaze at the food stalls and wonder if I will ever feast from their likes again, to say nothing of the crowded taverns where I could afford nary a plate to eat off of. Perhaps my woes would be solved if I were to grow my own food? If I dared to try that, however, I would need something to urge the plants along, lest I starve before they sprout.",
